body:
This PR adds support for ACTS v15 and leverages Spack's new conditional variant mechanism to greatly reduce the number of conflict statements (which were formerly used to encode "this variant exists since ACTS version N" and "variant X depends on variant Y" facts).

~~I'll keep it as a draft while it's undergoing a test build, and if it builds on my side I think it's good to go.~~

@wdconinc FYI.
